I heard that 3-4 times and fell in love with this song. I did not asked him what is that song as I believed that if that song has to come in my life it will come eventually.  Just a day after we finished thw trip here is the song auto populated on my youtube list screen. 

Beautiful song and lucky arethose who have daughter. ❤❤
